race.comment: EDGE OF FAITH (7) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a third place finish (19.48) at Temora two back. Can make amends. ZIPPING KIMMICH (2) is having his first look at this track. Comes here after a last start 4th and beaten 7 lengths (26.16) at Temora. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Bold showing expected. LINE BREAKER (1) was below best at his last couple, the latest finishing eighth at this track, but was among the placings at Temora three back. Well placed here and can atone this time. BLUE SWALLOW (8) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.
